'''飓风弗洛伊德'''（{{lang-en|Hurricane Floyd}}）是[[1987年大西洋飓风季|1987年大西洋飓风季]]中唯一[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]美国的飓风，也是该季最后一场获命名的风暴，于10月9日在[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]东岸近海发展形成。成为热带风暴后，气旋北上穿越[[古巴|古巴]]西部。受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响，弗洛伊德意外转向东北，于10月12日晚在[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]附近达到飓风强度。风暴经过佛罗里达州南部，催生出两场[[龙卷风|龙卷风]]并引发轻度破坏，还在德克萨斯州南部产生[[离岸流|离岸潮]]并夺走一条人命。弗洛伊德只在飓风强度下保持12小时，然后就因冷锋导致外界环境不利而减弱。气旋经过[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]并逐渐转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，最终于10月14日逐渐消散。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Floyd 1987 track.png}}
飓风弗洛伊德的源头可以追溯到10月5日[[洪都拉斯湾|洪都拉斯湾]]内的[[低气压|低气压区]]。这片天气系统接下来几天里向东飘移，之后又转向南下抵达[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]东岸近海。10月9日，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机确认低气压区内发展出有组织的[[大气环流|环流]]，表明第十三号热带低气压已经形成。气旋继续向南飘移，然后因东侧有[[高压脊|高压脊]]形成转向北上，之后又转朝西北方向前进。受高空的[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响，热带低气压逐渐组织，于10月10日增强成热带风暴并获名“弗洛伊德”（{{lang|en|Floyd}}）。<ref name="tcr">{{cite report | author = Gilbert C. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Preliminary Report (Page 1) | publisher = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | accessdate = 2011-07-13 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304024026/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim01.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim01.gif | format = [[GIF|GIF]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>

达到热带风暴标准后，气旋因受逐渐逼近的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响而在西加勒比海加速北上。弗洛伊德稳步增强，于10月12日清晨进入古巴最西侧上空。<ref name="tcr" />气象机构起初预测风暴会在[[那不勒斯_(佛罗里达州)|那不勒斯]]和[[麦尔兹堡|麦尔兹堡]]之间[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，但气旋实际上却出人意料地大幅转向东北进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]东南部。<ref name="tcr3">{{cite report | author = Gilbert C. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Preliminary Report (Page 3) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2011-07-14 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002022441/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim03.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim03.gif | deadurl = no }}</ref>根据飓风猎人侦察机的报告，气象部门认定弗洛伊德于10月12日短暂达到飓风标准。与此同时，附近的冷锋催生出冷气压区，导致风暴的[[内流_(气象学)|内流]]中断。气旋经过[[佛罗里达礁岛群|佛罗里达礁岛群]]，成为这年吹袭美国的唯一一场飓风，但在冷锋的影响下，中心上空的对流在此期间迅速消退，不久后就降级成热带风暴。[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]无法再通过卫星图像追踪环流，<ref name="tcr" />只有地面观测结果表明弗洛伊德从[[迈阿密|迈阿密]]以南不远处经过。风暴在[[巴哈马|巴哈马]]上空减弱并逐渐转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，到10月18日晚已完成转变。次日清晨，环流在冷锋范围内完全消散。<ref name="tcr2">{{cite report | author = Gilbert C. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Hurricane Floyd Preliminary Report (Page 2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304090102/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim02.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim02.gif | format = GIF | deadurl = no }}</ref>

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Floyd_1987_rainfall.gif|200px]]

弗洛伊德刚刚达到热带风暴强度时，[[天鹅群岛|天鹅群岛]]和[[大开曼|大开曼]]收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴警告]]。此后不久，[[尤卡坦半岛|尤卡坦半岛]]东北部接获热带风暴警告和飓风观察预警，气旋之后在该半岛沿海地区降下暴雨<ref name="warn" /><ref>{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | title = Storms Cause Heavy Rains | newspaper = The Victoria Advocate | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | date = 1987-10-11 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YNFdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Jl4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=2618,2800798&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209170112/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=YNFdAAAAIBAJ&sjid=Jl4NAAAAIBAJ&pg=2618%2C2800798&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。古巴[[哈瓦那|哈瓦那]]以西地区也进入热带风暴警告或飓风观察预警生效状态<ref name="warn">{{cite report | author = Gilbert C. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Table 3. Watches and Warnings for Hurricane Floyd, October 1987 | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | format = GIF | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002022454/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim09.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim09.gif | deadurl = no }}</ref>。面对风暴来袭，古巴[[比那尔德里奥省|比那尔德里奥省]]官员将约十万居民和四万头牛转移。此外，还有多架国际航班在弗洛伊德过境期间取消<ref name="dispatch">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | date = 1987-10-12 | title = Storm gains strength, nears Florida | newspaper = The Dispatch | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=KjseAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AL8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=5373,5281821&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209170121/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=KjseAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AL8EAAAAIBAJ&pg=5373%2C5281821&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。气旋以热带风暴强度经过古巴西部，但没有在该国造成重大破坏或人员丧生<ref name="tcr3" />。

热带风暴弗洛伊德位于古巴上空时，美国国家飓风中心向佛罗里达礁岛群和该州西南沿海至[[威尼斯_(佛罗里达州)|威尼斯]]发布飓风警告。这是佛罗里达州首次收到与这场风暴有关的警告，气象机构预计气旋会在短时间内增强成飓风。<ref name="tcr3" />该州东部接获热带风暴观察预警，之后又升级成警告<ref name="warn1" />。随着弗洛伊德的移动路线朝东偏移，佛罗里达州东南部和巴哈马西北部也收到飓风警告<ref name="tcr3" /><ref name="warn1">{{cite report | author = Gilbert C. Clark | date = 1987-10-27 | title = Table 3. Watches and Warnings for Hurricane Floyd, October 1987 (page 2) | publisher = National Hurricane Center | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | archivedate = 2015-10-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20151002022455/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim10.gif | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/storm_wallets/atlantic/atl1987-prelim/floyd/prelim10.gif | format = GIF }}</ref>。面对气旋威胁，佛罗里达州南部官员将学校关闭<ref name="dispatch" />，[[迈阿密国际机场|迈阿密国际机场]]有少量航班取消。[[霍姆斯特德空军后备基地|霍姆斯特德空军基地]]约有100架[[F-4幽灵II战斗机|F-4]]和[[F-16战隼战斗机|F16战斗机]]转移到更加安全的地点。[[美国红十字会|美国红十字会]]在佛罗里达州的[[佛罗里达州行政区划|十个县]]开设有55个避难所，一度有约2000人前来躲避，其中大部分是在[[李县_(佛罗里达州)|李县]]。<ref name="sht2">{{cite news | author = Richard Cole | date = 1987-10-13 | title = Floyd Brushes Over Keys, Miami, Moves Out to Sea | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | agency = Associated Press | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3vMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rnIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4218,3919711&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209171647/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3vMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rnIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4218%2C3919711&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>飓风沿途地区居民从超市购买应急物资并为交通工具加好油，把室外的松散物品固定，以此应对风暴来袭<ref name="sht">{{cite news | author = Mark Zaloudek | date = 1987-10-13 | title = Floyd Misses Gulf Coast - Which Doesn't Miss Floyd | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3vMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rnIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4218,3919711&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209171647/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=3vMcAAAAIBAJ&sjid=rnIEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4218%2C3919711&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。

弗洛伊德是1985年的[[1985年飓风鲍勃|飓风鲍勃]]过后首场袭击佛罗里达州南部并获命名的风暴<ref name="star">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | agency = Associated Press | newspaper = Star-News | date = 1987-10-13 | title = Floyd rolls over Florida | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=t-JOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=FxQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6918,4829797&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209170336/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=t-JOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=FxQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=6918%2C4829797&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。气旋经过该州南部期间在海上和陆地上都产生强风，佛罗里达礁岛群以[[达克基_(佛罗里达州)|达克基]]（{{lang|en|Duck Key}}）持续风速最高，达到每小时94公里，并且阵风时速更高。位于[[库乔基_(佛罗里达州)|库乔基]]（{{lang|en|Cudjoe Key}}）的美国空军基地所测阵风时速高达152公里，但这个数字没有得到正式确认。弗洛伊德的[[雨带|雨带]]直接产生的降水不到25毫米，但飓风同逐渐逼近的冷锋相互影响，产生的降雨量要高得多。<ref name="tcr2" />降雨范围向北面一直延伸到[[戴通纳海滩|戴通纳海滩]]，并以[[匹尔斯堡_(佛罗里达州)|匹尔斯堡]]雨量最高，达256毫米<ref>{{cite web | author = David Roth | publisher = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | date = 2005-09-25 | title = Hurricane Floyd - October 10-13, 1987 | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain//floyd1987.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304084430/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/floyd1987.html | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。风暴绕过佛罗里达礁岛群期间催生出的[[海龙卷风|海龙卷风]]在岩石港（{{lang|en|Rock Harbor}}）登岸，造成少量船只和民宅受损<ref name="tcr2" />。风暴还在遥远的[[德克萨斯州|德克萨斯州]]沿海产生[[离岸流|离岸潮]]，导致[[南帕诸岛|南帕诸岛]]（{{lang|en|South Padre Island}}）一人遇难<ref>{{cite news | title = Hurricane Floyd causes riptide along Texas coast | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = The Bonham Daily Favorite | agency = Associated Press | date = 1987-10-13 | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=T8Y9AAAAIBAJ&sjid=NDcMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1514,1956753&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en | archive-date = 2022-02-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220209173133/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=T8Y9AAAAIBAJ&sjid=NDcMAAAAIBAJ&pg=1514%2C1956753&dq=floyd+tropical&hl=en }}</ref>。

弗洛伊德在佛罗里达州南部大范围地区引发轻度破坏，损失总额约为50万美元（1987年美元）<ref>{{cite journal | author1 = Robert A. Case | author2 = Harold Gerrish | date = 1988-04 | volume = 116 | publisher = American Meteorological Society | journal = Monthly Weather Review | title = Atlantic Hurricane Season of 1987 | accessdate = 2016-10-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304040405/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/general/lib/lib1/nhclib/mwreviews/1987.pdf | format = PDF | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | bibcode = 1988MWRv..116..939C | doi = 10.1175/1520-0493(1988)116<0939:AHSO>2.0.CO;2 }}</ref>，其中大部分属树木倒塌和电缆受损，[[迈阿密-戴德县|戴德县]]的农作物遭受轻微损失<ref name="tcr3" />。佛罗里达州南部多条道路被降水产生的洪水淹没，导致州收费公路上许多车辆抛锚<ref name="dispatch" />。吹袭佛罗里达州后，弗洛伊德又对巴哈马造成轻度风害<ref name="tcr3" />。该国以[[弗里波特_(巴哈马)|弗里波特]]（{{lang|en|Freeport}}）所测阵风时速最高，达到77公里。风暴残留在[[大巴哈马国际机场|弗里波特国际机场]]产生的持续风速约为每小时64公里。<ref name="News2">{{cite news | author = Staff Writer | newspaper = Miami Herald | date = 1987-10-14 | accessdate = 2009-07-03 | title = Floyd Nicks Bahamas, Fades Into Oblivion | url = http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB368311EDA2AF6&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date:D&s_trackval=GooglePM | archive-date = 2020-09-06 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200906105034/http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=MH&s_site=miami&p_multi=MH&p_theme=realcities&p_action=search&p_maxdocs=200&p_topdoc=1&p_text_direct-0=0EB368311EDA2AF6&p_field_direct-0=document_id&p_perpage=10&p_sort=YMD_date%3AD&s_trackval=GooglePM | dead-url = no }}</ref>

